umptown-tops-freshman-series-premieres-in-overall-raw-gains/|title= Live+7 Weekly Ratings: \u2018Stumptown\u2019 Tops Freshman Series Premieres in Overall Raw Gains|last=Pucci|first=Douglas|date=October 8, 2019|website=ProgrammingInsider.com |accessdate=October 8, 2019}}</ref>\n\n| title2   = [[#ep79|Testimonials]]\n| date2    = October 3, 2019\n| rs2      = 0.8/4\n| viewers2 = 2.78<ref name=\"5.02\"/>\n| dvr2     = 0.4\n| total2   = 1.1<ref>{{cite web|url=https://programminginsider.com/live7-weekly-ratings-emergence-leads-broadcast-network-telecasts-in-viewer-percentage-gains/|title=Live+7 Weekly Ratings: \u2018Emergence\u2019 Leads Broadcast Network Telecasts in Viewer Percentage Gains|last=Pucci|first=Douglas|date=October 15, 2019|website=Programming Insider|accessdate=October 15, 2019}}</ref>\n\n| title3   = [[#ep80|Forced Hire]]\n| date3    = October 10, 2019\n| rs3      = 0.8/4\n| viewers3 = 2.79<ref name=\"5.03\"/>\n| dvr3     = n/a\n| total3   = n/a\n\n| title4   = [[#ep81|Mall Closing]]\n| date4    = October 17, 2019\n| rs4      = 0.8/4\n| viewers4 = 2.94<ref name=\"5.04\"/>\n| dvr4     = 0.5\n| total4   = 1.3<ref>{{cite web|url=https://programminginsider.com/live7-weekly-ratings-nancy-drew-and-riverdale-top-broadcast-network-telecasts-in-adults-18-49-percentage-gains/|title=Live+7 Weekly Ratings: \u2018Nancy Drew\u2019 and \u2018Riverdale\u2019 Top Broadcast Network Telecasts in Adults 18-49 Percentage Gains|last=Pucci|first=Douglas|date=October 30, 2019|website=Programming Insider|accessdate=November 1, 2019}}</ref>\n\n| title5   = [[#ep82|Self-Care]]\n| date5    = October 24, 2019\n| rs5      = 0.8/4\n| viewers5 = 2.84<ref name=\"5.05\"/>\n| dvr5     = 0.3\n| total5   = 1.1<ref>{{cite web|url=https://programminginsider.com/live7-weekly-ratings-supergirl-leads-broadcast-network-entries-in-adults-18-49-percentage-lifts/|title=Live+7 Weekly Ratings: \u2018Supergirl\u2019 Leads Broadcast Network Entries in Adults 18-49 Percentage Lifts|last=Pucci|first=Dougl