://www.instagram.com/p/B0yg04OgJhP/|title=Today is the first day of filming for season 5 of #Superstore!|work=Instagram|date=August 5, 2019|accessdate=August 25, 2019}}</ref> The season premiered on September 26, 2019 on [[NBC]]. The series continues to air in its Thursday at 8:00 PM timeslot.<ref name=\"2019 Premiere\">{{cite web|url=https://tvline.com/2019/08/16/superstore-season-5-preview-poster-key-art-nbc/|title=Superstore Crew Rages Against the Machine in Season 5 Poster|last=Schwartz|first=Ryan|publisher=[[TVLine]]|date=August 16, 2019|accessdate=August 25, 2019}}</ref> The season was set to contain 22 episodes,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2019/11/05/nbc-orders-four-more-episodes-of-its-hit-comedy-superstore-bringing-the-season-total-to-22-473114/20191105nbc05/|title=NBC Orders Four More Episodes of Its Hit Comedy \"Superstore,\" Bringing the Season Total to 22|publisher=[[The Futon Critic]]|date=November 5, 2019|accessdate=November 5, 2019}}</ref> however production was shut down after the completion of the 21st episode due to the [[2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://tvline.com/2020/03/14/superstore-season-5-finale-america-ferrera-leaving-amy/|title=Superstore Cuts Season Short Due to Coronavirus \u2014 Will America Ferrera's Amy Get a Proper Farewell?|first=Michael|last=Ausiello|work=TVLine|date=March 14, 2020|accessdate=March 15, 2020}}</ref>\n\n''Superstore'' follows a group of employees working at Cloud 9, a fictional [[big-box store]] in [[St. Louis]], [[Missouri]]. The ensemble and supporting cast features [[America Ferrera]], [[Ben Feldman (actor)|Ben Feldman]], [[Lauren Ash]], [[Colton Dunn]], [[Nico Santos (actor)|Nico Santos]], [[Nichole Bloom]], [[Mark McKinney]], and [[Kaliko Kauahi]]. Kauahi joins the regular cast after being credited as a recurring character in seasons 1\u20134.\n\n==Cast==\n===Main===\n*[[America Ferrera]] as Amy Sosa \n*[[Ben Feldman (actor)|Ben Feldman]] as Jonah Simms\n*[[Lauren Ash]] as Dina Fox\n*[[Colton Dunn]] as Garrett McNeil\n*[[Nico Santos (actor)|Nico Santos]] as Mateo Fernando Aquino Liwanag\n*[[Nichole Bloom]] as Cheyenne Thompson\n*[[Kaliko Kauahi]] as Sandra Kaluiokalani\n*[[Mark McKinney]] as Glenn Sturgis\n\n===Recurring===\n* Jon Barinholtz as Marcus White\n* [[Kelly Stables]] as Kelly Watson\n* Kelly Schumann as Justine Sikowitz\n* Irene White as Carol<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/B1ZsvdmJnFh/|title=There she is.|work=Instagram|date=August 21, 2019|accessdate=August 25, 2019}}</ref>\n* Amir M. Korangy as Sayid\n* [[Michael Bunin]] as Jeff Sutton\n* Chris Grace as Jerry\n* [[Justina Machado]] as Maya<ref name=\"update\">{{cite web|url=https://tvline.com/2019/08/28/superstore-season-5-justina-machado-cast-new-district-manager/|title=Superstore Season 5: Justina Machado to Recur, SNL's Heidi Gardner Also Cast|last=Schwartz|first=Ryan|publisher=[[TVLine]]|date=August 28, 2019|accessdate=August 29, 2019}}</ref>\n* [[David Wain]] as Dan the Optometrist\n\n===Guest cast===\n* [[Johnny Pemberton]] as Bo Derek Thompson<ref>Pemberton has appeared in at least two episodes of this season thus far.</ref>\n* [[Heidi Gardner]] as Colleen<ref name=\"update\" />\n* [[Kerri Kenney-Silver]] as Jerusha Sturgis\n* [[Jerry Minor]] as Richard\n* [[Fred Armisen]] as Kyle\n* [[George Salazar]] as Eric Sosa\n* [[Ian Gomez]] as Herb\n* [[Dean Norris]] as Howard Fox\n* [[Scott MacArthur]] as Benny\n\n==Episodes==\n{{See also|List of Superstore episodes}}\n<onlyinclude>{{Episode table |background=#6A9BCF |overall=5 |season=5 |title=18 |director=16 |writer=24 |airdate=18 |airdateR=<ref name=\"futon\">{{cite web|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/showatch/superstore/listings/ |title=Listings, Superstore on NBC |work=The Futon Critic |accessdate=September 13, 2019}}</ref> |viewers=13 |country=U.S. |episodes=\n{{Episode list/sublist|Superstore (season 5)\n |EpisodeNumber = 78\n |EpisodeNumber2 = 1\n |Title = Cloud 9.0\n |Directed